## Commercial Add-On Terms

### Marketplace Packs & Templates

Commercial marketplace packs, premium templates, and brand kits distributed 
via the FlashFusion marketplace are subject to separate commercial licenses:

- **Creator Toolkit Pack**: Proprietary - Commercial license required
- **E-commerce Storefront Pack**: Proprietary - Commercial license required
- **Universal App Scaffold**: Proprietary - Commercial license required

These commercial add-ons are NOT covered by the MIT license above and may not 
be redistributed, resold, or used in derivative works without explicit 
permission from FlashFusion.co.

### Third-Party Assets

Certain assets (fonts, icons, images) included in marketplace packs may be 
subject to their own licenses:

- **Sora Font**: Open Font License (OFL)
- **Inter Font**: Open Font License (OFL)
- **Lucide Icons**: ISC License
- **Generated AI Assets**: Subject to AI provider terms (see PROVENANCE.md)

### Commercial Usage

This software (excluding commercial add-ons) may be used for commercial 
purposes under the MIT license. However:

- AI generation features require API keys and comply with provider ToS
- Stripe integration requires Stripe account and compliance with Stripe ToS
- Supabase features require Supabase account and compliance with Supabase ToS

### Support & Warranty

Community support is provided via GitHub Issues. Commercial support contracts 
with SLA guarantees are available separately. Contact: support@flashfusion.co

